  [Text] Kuwait City, May 30 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Deputy 
Foreign Minister Tian Zenpei left here for Saudi Arabia today 
winding up a three-day working visit to Kuwait. 
  During his visit here, Tian held talks with a number of 
senior Kuwaiti officials on bilateral relations and regional and 
