  [Text] Article by Wen Jiabao: "It Is Necessary To Deepen 
Rural Reform and Promote Agriculture to New Heights" 
  Article by Wu Yi: "Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Should 
Be Developed on the Basis of Equality and Mutual Benefit" 
  Article by Lin Yanzhi, Dai Zhou, Zhao Baohua, and Xie 
Zhihua: 
"A Basic Project Which Helps Improve the Quality of the Chinese 
Nation" 
  Article by by Guo Qing: "Persist in Seeking Truth From 
Facts, Oppose the Practice of Deception" 
  Article by Li Shuzheng: "The Most Powerful Weapon To 
Understand the World Situation and Master International 
Strategy--Feelings After Studying Volume 3 of the Selected Works 
of Deng Xiaoping" 
  Article by Wei Xinghua and Wang Yuanlong: "On Macrocontrol 
and Regulation in the Socialist Market Economy" 
  Article by Zhang Fuyou: "It Is Necessary To Strengthen Staff 
Members' and Workers' Democratic Management and Promote the 
Profound Development of Reform" 
  Article by He Jianlin: "The Market Economy and the Concept 
of Overall Interests" 
  Article by Miao Yongxin: "`Three Guarantees in Enterprises' 
